author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I need to seal the gap between my drywall ceiling and framing. I'm using Great Stuff Wide Spray because it'll close that gap and prevent air from getting into the bathroom below. This, combined with insulation, will make the bathroom comfortable in the winter and the summer.
